OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be cloudy
OL,6,Fwith some rain, heavy at times. This
OL,7,Fafternoon will be drier with some
OL,8,Fbrightness breaking through along with
OL,9,Ffew showers.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening and the first
OL,12,Fpart of the night will see showers or
OL,13,Fsome longer spells of rain. Becoming
OL,14,Fdrier and clearer later in the night.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FAll parts will have a dry
OL,17,Fday with variable amounts of cloud and
OL,18,Fsunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
